---
// Simplified Novicompu Footer component (landing focus)
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#17243A] text-sm">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Adjusted to 3 columns after removing navigation -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 pb-10 pt-14">
      <!-- About -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-100 uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">Sobre</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-5 leading-relaxed">Novicompu, plataforma móvil para descubrir y comprar tecnología en Ecuador: laptops, smartphones, audio, gaming y más. Envíos rápidos y soporte local.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Recursos / Social -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-100 uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">Recursos</h4>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3">
          <li><a href="https://www.novicompu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors">Ecommerce</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/novicompu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors">Instagram</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/novicompu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors">Facebook</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@novicompu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors">TikTok</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Descarga -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-100 uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">Descarga</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-5">Obtén la app y accede a ofertas exclusivas y soporte rápido.</p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-col gap-3">
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="App Store" class="inline-block">
            <img src="/assets/images/store.png" alt="Descargar en App Store" class="h-12" />
          </a>
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Google Play" class="inline-block">
            <img src="/assets/images/google.png" alt="Disponible en Google Play" class="h-12" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="py-4 bg-[#1C2940]">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-0 justify-between items-center">
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-white">{year} © Novicompu - Todos los derechos reservados</p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <a aria-label="Instagram" href="https://www.instagram.com/novicompu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="size-8 inline-flex justify-center items-center rounded-md text-white hover:bg-[#264193] transition-colors"> 
